list.title: getDarkestColor
list.description:
Finds the darkest color from a given array of color objects based on the 'L' property.
It assumes the darkest color is represented by an 'L' property value of -100.

list.title: getNextIncrement
list.description: Increments a given positive number by a specified step and returns the result as a string, padded to a specified length with a given character.
